Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:06.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are distant creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:13.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Primitive and peculiar, they are {\i1}things{\i0} unlike\Nany animal or plant we've grown to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:23.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In time and with fear, Man has\Ncome to call them "Mushi".
