Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:42.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone strange is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:53.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:58.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear I just saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The greenery here is so vivid that it's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:12.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:22.95,ep-title-bg,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.03,0:02:22.95,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\be1}The Green Seat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally gifted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are those,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,every so often,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,who have the natural conditions\Nto summon life – water, plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.98,sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(770.8,170.2)\blur1\frz338.6\frx36\fry346}Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can at least {\i1}write{\i0} with my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sunlight is slowly becoming more bearable,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the leaves are turning red and the birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:03.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm left-handed anyway, so it's\Neasier for me to write this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shoot, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These characters are really drawings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hieroglyphics, as they're called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which is nice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, get back here, "bird"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't wander off outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:50.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be Ioroi Shinra-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get my letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:06.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, then you must be the Mushi-shi, Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just in the act of writing you a rejection letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:16.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've received several requests\Nfor investigation in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I rejected all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,By my grandmother's will,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Don't let others know of your abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and keep them hidden for as long as possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:32.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you've seen, when I make a depiction of some form,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:36.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,even an inanimate object comes to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:42.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it is not man's place to create new beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,for that would anger the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:50.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I was forbidden by my grandmother\Nto draw with my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:56.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing happens when I draw with my right hand,\Nbut I hurt my finger the other day, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you saw what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure took me by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It scared me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really had no idea that even words would come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen some really weird things come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Such as?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umbrellas, back scratchers, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,An investigation is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean that I'm going to make you leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have been tough coming\Nall the way up this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should rest here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's been a while since I've talked with anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'd love to chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made this berry wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I usually drink alone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You live alone in this isolated place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since my grandma died four years ago, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me that I couldn't leave this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:06.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Indeed, if this kid lived downtown and\Naccidentally brought something to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they wouldn't let him live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His abilities are way beyond human comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:19.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like your grandmother was a wise woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:20.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always looked out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:32.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you take a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you draw these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:41.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:46.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sort of come up with these things when I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always wondered what they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always loved watching them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'd draw them and show them to Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:03.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you always see these illusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:08.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must be because of your horrible powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must stop seeing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, how dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You poor child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:22.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She never believed what I saw, even to her last breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:32.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I sometimes thought that there really\Nmust be something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the one thing that I couldn't\Nshare with Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,these are all Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not quite like the insects we're accustomed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put bluntly, it's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:59.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say these four fingers are animals,\Nand my thumb is a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:05.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man is here, furthest away from the heart,\Nat the tip of the middle finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lower you are on the hand, the\Nmore primitive you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you trace them, the veins all\Nconverge around the wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bacteria and microbes are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:23.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this point, it's hard to distinguish\Nbetween plants and animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there are things even lower than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:29.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Up the arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,past the shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:41.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and here are the Mushi, or as others\Ncall them, the Midorimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are close to being merely essences of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:51.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And because they are, their shapes and existences are vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some people can see them, some people can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some of them are invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,like ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lot of the so-called "ghosts" are actually Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some can even pretend to be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your grandmother just couldn't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to share one's perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same way it's impossible to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,convey how something feels without them having felt it for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:31.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to understand something that can't\Nbe seen... let alone the world it lives in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:42.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, Grandma, I can't help but be happy\Nthat such things exist in our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm, where's the washroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sheesh, this house is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's old too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hard to believe he lives here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm, something just passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, not that I didn't expect Mushi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:23.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Mushi Pin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you stick Mushi onto that and put\Nthem up as decorations, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vile Mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:36.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk, Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh... What is this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a Mushi, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clings to its own kind and never lets go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't last long, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may be broken, but it's still a pretty wine cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you drinking under the moonlight or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, and give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shamelessly intruding into people's homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:18.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure are stuck-up for a Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People's homes, eh? Is this {\i1}your{\i0} home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:28.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:33.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one of those who used to be\Nhuman but acquired Mushi traits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you're so weak, because\Nyou're incomplete as a Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A chipped, green wine cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It tells me why you're the way you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:46.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:48.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Renzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I looked into Shinra's background\Nbefore I came up here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can tell you how to fix this wine cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:00.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma Renzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma's still in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, not as a human, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's here as a half human, half Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How... can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a phenomenon known as a "Mushi Banquet".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's when Mushi pretend to be human
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and invite guests to their parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guest is given a cup of wine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and when they drink the whole cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,they lose their identity as a sentient being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:47.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, they become inhabitants\Nof the world of the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:52.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the banquet was cut short,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and your grandma was fortunate\Nenough to not turn into a Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Grandma, when she returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,was no longer the Grandma she was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She left half of herself in the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:10.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinra,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Grandma you knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,was only half of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the other half of her was always here too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:23.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,watching over you ever since the day you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't see her because she's not a complete Mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:40.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but with your ability, we can make her a complete Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:45.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to come back to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,see Shinra that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your grandma didn't hesitate for very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:10.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} help her, right, Shinra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't watch me while I draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:20.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Shinra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:27.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Draw the wine cup Grandma was holding as\NI explained earlier, with your left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:31.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? But I don't know what color it is or what it even looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just use your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:37.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other half of the wine cup\Nyour grandmother received
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,should be passed on to her children and grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He told me not to watch him, but\Ndoes he really think I wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Green. I think it's green.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:06.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rich, vibrant green like the green of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:13.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's flat and round.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:21.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's splitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Renzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you there, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, drink it, Renzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you two blushing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, she was younger than I thought and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, have some too, to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:32.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:37.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Grandma's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should hurry, the sun's setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:48.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't get out of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:43.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, drink, Ioroi Renzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This banquet is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How fragrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With every sip,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lose my ability to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is a creature called Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It dwells deep in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and forms an enormous stream of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:23.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We created for you a unique wine cup\Nthat can extract from that stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:28.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the day life was born, it has existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:34.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Life grows strong where it is close\Nand dries up when it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, it is the water of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:40.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing in this world is more delicious than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:48.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is because we have a request of you that we\Ntreat you with this wine and such hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:53.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thirty-one years from now, a grandson\Nwill be born to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:59.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,with a unique ability with which he\Nmay change the entire living world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wish for you to look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:11.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ability will be a blessing both unto\Nyour grandson and this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:17.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that is your wish, we will give you strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:21.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, finish the rest of the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:47.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinra's tears would not stop flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:35.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Renzu's senses, her emotions, had flowed into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:38.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:44.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sad that the wine cup broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:49.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as if in sympathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kouki flowed out of the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,it flowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, there's moss everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:16.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everywhere the Kouki soaked in last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to give up on that "investigation" of Shinra?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:21.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that his pesky guardian is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should drop by some time, as long\Nas you don't do an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinra must be lonely being here by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:44.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,now that you'll always be by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:49.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:54.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, he didn't even say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't have a chance to thank him, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:07.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the green wine cup's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:20.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard no more about the child\Nwith God's left hand ever since.
